title: Vikings' Fisseha player of week
text:
Vikings' Fisseha player of week By: Uncredited Report Error 
Linebacker Joel Fisseha of the Vincent Massey Vikings has been named the defensive player of the week in the Kas Vidruk (AA) Division of the Winnipeg High School Football League. 
Fisseha was honoured after making seven tackles, forcing a fumble and recovering a fumble in Massey’s 32-7 win over Kildonan East last Friday.
